00:04:14.780 --> 00:04:20.490
We don't know that, but if we can
create spaces that are accessible

00:04:20.490 --> 00:04:25.780
and also really well designed
for multiple disabilities,

00:04:25.780 --> 00:04:28.670
and of course for all the users
that will access your content,

00:04:28.670 --> 00:04:31.620
that is the best.

