00:04:59.190 --> 00:05:00.880
And let us think about that.

00:05:00.880 --> 00:05:04.510
So we are professionals,
we know our thing, right?

00:05:04.510 --> 00:05:06.080
We know what we need to do.

00:05:06.080 --> 00:05:10.720
We are good designers, we are
good developers, project managers,

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:11.860
et cetera.

00:05:11.860 --> 00:05:16.450
But sometimes we forget that we
also need to follow certain laws,

00:05:16.450 --> 00:05:19.190
standards,
et cetera around the world

00:05:19.190 --> 00:05:21.090
in order to create
our sites accessible.

00:05:22.730 --> 00:05:28.260
Finally, sometimes we have a
