for a company where, usually,

00:47:49.880 --> 00:47:56.900
the data or the visualization
that you are creating implies

00:47:56.900 --> 00:48:00.374
that the audience be
highly technically skilled,

00:48:00.375 --> 00:48:04.137
you need to think about
types of disability

00:48:04.138 --> 00:48:07.130
that are not necessarily physical,

00:48:08.190 --> 00:48:14.270
like learning disabilities or
cognitive disabilities, right?

00:48:14.270 --> 00:48:15.840
So this is really important.

00:48:15.840 --> 00:48:18.150
